---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Senior Shopware Frontend Developer (m/f/d)" description="We are looking for a Senior Shopware Frontend Developer (m/f/d) – Hob by Horse GmbH, Osnabrück.">
	<div class="job-page">
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="hero-inner">
				<p class="kicker">Jobs</p>
				<h1>Senior Shopware Frontend Developer (m/f/d)</h1>
				<p class="subheadline">hob or flop</p>
				<p class="intro">Come for the joy to Osnabrück. Work-life balance isn't just a phrase here. We are looking for a Senior Shopware Frontend Developer (m/f/d) to support our teams immediately.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div class="content">

			<h3>Your Responsibilities</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Template development based on Shopware 6</li>
				<li>Implementation of layouts and designs</li>
				<li>Independent development of custom plugins</li>
				<li>You are up to the analysis, planning and implementation of complex development tasks and create a continuous exchange of experience</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>You Bring Some of These Qualities</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Very good knowledge of JavaScript, CSS, HTML and Bootstrap 4</li>
				<li>Good knowledge of CSS preprocessors such as Less</li>
				<li>Good knowledge of the template engine Twig</li>
				<li>Very good knowledge of current web standards, e.g. ECMAScript 2015</li>
				<li>Experience with VCS, ideally GIT</li>
				<li>Ideally experience with Jira</li>
				<li>Knowledge of VueJS</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>What We Offer You</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>You work for well-known clients &amp; brands</li>
				<li>Exciting clients and varied projects</li>
				<li>Intensive exchange: learning, contributing and sharing your own knowledge</li>
				<li>We introduce you to projects at a relaxed pace and won't throw you in at the deep end</li>
				<li>A genuine 40-hour week: we respect you and your free time greatly, which is why you can choose your holiday dates freely and at short notice</li>
				<li>Flexible working hours – come and go earlier or later, or work from home</li>
				<li>Quiet working environment in small offices</li>
				<li>We want to develop you and support you with all necessary measures (training, webinars, certificates &amp; more)</li>
				<li>Best workplace equipment: MacBook and Linux. The choice is yours!</li>
				<li>Long-term prospects</li>
				<li>Great team! We stand up for each other – and go on a big trip together once a year</li>
				<li>Flat hierarchies, short and fast decision-making paths and room to develop yourself</li>
			</ul>

			<p class="cta-text">All clear? We look forward to your straightforward contact by email at <a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de">info@hob-by-horse.de</a>. Of course we are also available in advance for any questions you may have. Please send us your application with your salary expectations preferably by email as a PDF. If you can, we would love to see examples of your previous experience.</p>

			<a href="mailto:info@hob-by-horse.de?subject=Application: Senior Shopware Frontend Developer" class="apply-btn">Apply now</a>

		</div>
	</div>
</Base>

<style>
	.job-page { background: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; min-height: 100vh; }
	.hero { padding-top: var(--header-height); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
	.hero-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0; padding: var(--spacing-3xl) var(--spacing-xl); }
	h1 { font-size: clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.5rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #00b4d8; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); text-align: left; }
	.subheadline { font-size: var(--font-size-lg); font-weight: 700; color: #E7007F; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg); text-align: left; }
	.intro { font-size: var(--font-size-lg); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.75; text-align: left; max-width: none; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; }
	.content { max-width: 800px; margin: 0; padding: var(--spacing-3xl) var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-4xl); }
	h3 { font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: 700; color: #E7007F; margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md); text-align: left !important; }
	ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl); }
	li { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.7; padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm); text-align: left; }
	li::before { content: "#"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #E7007F; font-weight: 700; }
	.cta-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl); text-align: left !important; max-width: none !important; margin-left: 0 !important; margin-right: 0 !important; }
	.cta-text a { color: #00b4d8; text-decoration: none; }
	.cta-text a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
	.apply-btn { display: inline-block; padding: var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-2xl); background: #E7007F; color: #ffffff; font-size: var(--font-size-sm); font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.04em; transition: opacity 0.2s ease; }
	.apply-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
</style>
